# Tracked TUI snapshot baseline — CI-authoritative PNG key-frames.
#
# Populated and kept current by .github/workflows/vhs-baseline.yml (renders on
# ubuntu-latest so every committed frame comes from the same environment).
# Seed it after this lands by running that workflow once: `gh workflow run
# vhs-baseline.yml`. Feature PRs diff their renders against these via a per-PR
# vhs-captures/pr-<n> branch (.github/workflows/vhs-capture.yml).
#
# Regenerate locally (frames will differ from CI by platform): scripts/tui-vhs.sh --snapshot
